name: Time Shuttle (Kenney Jam 2018)
description:
This is a participated game for Kenney Jam 2018 (Theme: Time Travel)
This game is very simple. 
Click "Boost" to boost the rocket to a different speed.
Click "Land" to stop at the time you want.

Click "Collection" in the Home Screen to see what you'v found in the past.

And then 
Discover the historical moment at the landed time.
